<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.6">
<l>taṉkuṭik kētun takkavā niṉaiyāḷ taṭaṅkaṭal nuṭaṅkeyi lilaṅkai</l>
<l>vaṉkuṭi maṭaṅka vāḷamar tolaitta vārttaikēṭ ṭiṉpuṟum mayaṅkum</l>
<l>miṉkoṭi maruṅkul curuṅkamēl neruṅki meṉmulai poṉpayan tirunta</l>
<l>veṉkoṭi yivaḷuk keṉṉiṉain tiruntā yiṭaventai yentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She does not properly consider anything for her clan.</l>
<l rend="indent">She feels delight hearing the word that ended the cruel battle</l>
<l>So that the strong clan yielded Lanka, its walls shaken by the vast sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">[And] she swoons.</l>
<l>What were you intending, lord father of Iṭaventai, for my creeper girl,</l>
<l>Whose soft breasts have turned sallow, bearing down [from] above</l>
<l rend="indent">as her lightning-thin waist dwindles?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
